<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>@ViewBag.Title - Career Solutions</title>
    @section Styles {
        <style>
            body {
                font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
                margin: 0;
                padding: 0;
                background-image: url('/Content/assets/img/about/pictures/about3.jpg'); /* Add the URL of your background image here */
                background-size: cover; /* Cover the entire background */
                background-position: center; /* Center the background image */
            }

            .container {
                max-width: 1200px;
                margin: 0 auto;
                padding: 20px;
            }

            h2 {
                color: #333;
            }

            p {
                line-height: 1.6;
                color: #666;
            }
        </style>
    }
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h2>@ViewBag.Title Career Solutions</h2>
        <p>
            Career Solutions is a leading job consultancy company with a proven track record. We pride ourselves on connecting
            job seekers with the best employment opportunities. With our new online job portal, we aim to make job searching
            more efficient and seamless for both employers and job seekers.
        </p>
        <p>
            Whether you're a job seeker or an employer, our platform is designed to provide a user-friendly experience,
            offering personalized job recommendations, easy job postings, and an advanced matching system.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
